params.prompt: A full-body cyberpunk warrior, {{step1.output.age}} years old, {{step1.output.gender}}, of {{step1.output.race}} descent, standing fully facing the camera, with a clearly visible and well-defined face, neon cybernetic enhancements, futuristic armor, glowing mechanical implants, cinematic lighting, highly detailed. NO NSFW

A cyberpunk warrior stands firm in a neon-lit city, eyes scanning the surroundings. They shift stance, crack their knuckles, and activate glowing cybernetic implants. A sudden energy surge powers up their mechanical arm as they roll their shoulders, preparing for battle. Sparks fly as they draw a high-tech weapon, tilting their head slightly with a confident smirk. Holographic lights flicker around them, casting dynamic reflections. Smooth, cinematic motion, highly detailed.

A futuristic cyberpunk city at night, filled with neon lights, distant sirens, and the hum of hovering vehicles. The warrior’s mechanical arm emits a soft whirring sound as it powers up. Footsteps echo on wet pavement, accompanied by the subtle hiss of steam vents. Electric energy crackles as cybernetic implants activate. A distant explosion rumbles, sending a low-frequency shockwave. The warrior exhales sharply, adjusting their stance. Synthwave music pulses faintly in the background, blending with the ambient hum of the neon-lit streets.
